<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0785a25shiZhiXian"><lb
ed="T" n="0785a25"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0785a25"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date><placeName key="PL000000025341">鄧州香嚴山</placeName><persName key="A005255">智閑</persName>傳（<persName key="A009447">大同</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0785a26"/><persName key="A005255">釋智閑</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000021111">青州</placeName>人也。身裁七<anchor xml:id="beg0785sgsz3"/>尺<anchor xml:id="end0785sgsz3"/>，博聞強記，有幹<lb
ed="T" n="0785a27"/>略。親黨觀其所以，謂<ref type="person" target="#A005255">之</ref>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A005255">汝</ref>加力學，則他<lb
ed="T" n="0785a28"/>後成佐時之良器也。」俄爾，辭親出俗。既而<lb
ed="T" n="0785a29"/>慕法心堅，至南方<anchor xml:id="beg0785sgsz4"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0785sgsz4"/><placeName key="PL000000028694">溈山</placeName><persName key="A001984">大圓禪師</persName>盛會，<pb ed="T" n="0785b" xml:id="T50.2061.0785b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0785b01"/>咸推<persName key="A005255">閑</persName>為俊敏。<persName key="A001984">溈山</persName>一日召對，茫然。將諸<lb
ed="T" n="0785b02"/>方語要一時煨燼，曰：「畫餅弗可充飢也。」便<lb
ed="T" n="0785b03"/>望<placeName key="PL000000025497">南陽</placeName><persName key="A001707">忠<roleName>國師</roleName></persName>遺跡而居。偶芟除草木，擊<lb
ed="T" n="0785b04"/>瓦礫，失笑，冥有所證，抒頌唱之，由茲盛<lb
ed="T" n="0785b05"/>化<ptr target="#n1696"/>。終後，勅諡<persName key="A005255">襲燈大師</persName>，塔號<name><anchor xml:id="beg0785sgsz6"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>廷</sic><corr>延</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0785sgsz6"/><ptr target="#n1697"/>福</name>焉。次<placeName key="PL000000015565">舒<lb
ed="T" n="0785b06"/>州桐城投子山</placeName><persName key="A009447">釋大同</persName>，姓<name>劉</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000015479">舒州懷寧</placeName>人<lb
ed="T" n="0785b07"/>也。幼性剛正，有老成氣度。因投<placeName key="PL000000023575">洛下保唐</placeName><persName key="A010671">滿<lb
ed="T" n="0785b08"/>禪師</persName>出俗，初習安般觀<ptr target="#n1630"/>，業垂成，遂求華嚴<lb
ed="T" n="0785b09"/>性海。復負錫謁<placeName key="PL000000042513">翠微山</placeName>法會，同<placeName key="PL000000025190">伏牛</placeName><persName key="A010676">元通</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0785b10"/>激發請益，大明祖意。由是放蕩周遊，還歸故<lb
ed="T" n="0785b11"/>土，隱<placeName key="PL000000015565">投子山</placeName>，結茅茨，棲泊以求其志。<date from-iso="+0881-08-13" key="j20430642044395" to-iso="+0885-04-05"><name>中和</name></date><lb
ed="T" n="0785b12"/>中，<persName key="A008599">巢</persName>寇蕩<anchor xml:id="beg0785002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>履</sic><corr>覆</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0785002"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">京畿</placeName><ptr target="#n1698"/>，天下悖亂。有賊徒持刃<lb
ed="T" n="0785b13"/>問<persName key="A009447">同</persName>曰：「住此何為？」對以佛法。魁渠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1638"/>聞<anchor xml:id="beg0785sgsz8"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>面</sic><corr>而</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0785sgsz8"/>膜<lb
ed="T" n="0785b14"/>拜，脫身服裝而施之，下山。以<date key="j20550192055019" when-iso="+0914-05-08">梁<name>乾化</name>四年<lb
ed="T" n="0785b15"/>甲<anchor xml:id="beg0785sgsz10"/>戌<anchor xml:id="end0785sgsz10"/>四月六日</date>，加趺坐亡，春秋九十六，法臘<lb
ed="T" n="0785b16"/>四十六<ptr target="#n1699"/>。凡居化此山三十餘載云。</p>
